== 退休后的生活 ==
他成为一家跨国安全公司的首席运营官，该公司被称为“多业务安全机构情报公司”。<ref>{{cite web|first=Biba |last=Adams|date=2020-11-30|url=https://news.yahoo.com/former-station-chief-darrell-blocker-141840211.html |title=Former station chief Darrell Blocker being considered for CIA director: report |publisher=Yahoo |access-date=2020-11-30}}</ref><ref name="auto1"/>2019年8月，布洛克作为撰稿人加入ABC新闻。<ref name="abcnews" /><ref name=abcnews/>目前居于加州[[圣莫尼卡|圣莫尼卡]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://tiger21.com/presenter/darrell-blocker-mosaic-multi-operational-security-agency-intelligence-company/|title=Darrell Blocker|publisher=tiger21.com}}</ref>

